Chart with no name field in Chart.yaml. The parser falls back to the directory name as the release name.

-- Chart.yaml --
apiVersion: v2
description: A chart with no name
version: 0.1.0
-- templates/pod.yaml --
apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: test-pod
spec:
  containers:
    - name: app
      image: nginx
